title: I’m just a Superman - Novel Updates
tags: Fanfiction   Male Protagonist   Special Abilities   Transmigration
author: 凛冬纪元
description:
I’m just an ordinary superman.

Every morning, when the first rays of sunlight dawn on the ground, I will appear in the sunshine on time.

When the last glow of the evening disappeared, I will disappear again.

Occasionally, I will take a look at what kind of drama this dramatic world can perform for me.

But why, obviously I am just an audience, why do you always want me to join in?

Well, in that case, here I am!>
